node.text:
Guess who is sporty now?! So beyond honored to be part of this amazing new journey with @weareangelcity and @curateur ✨ This amazing football club is a part of the National Women’s Soccer League and our mission through this partnership is to showcase women-owned businesses and help educate, uplift and support other women as they impact our world. 💕⚽️XoRZ #CURATEUR
Repost from @weareangelcity
•
Curating opportunities for future generations starts here 👏

Together with @curateur, we’ll ensure that women feel their best as they make their mark both on and off the field.

node.text:
My heart breaks for #dauntewright his mother, his young son and his entire family. No mother should have to experience what she did on the other end of the phone. 💔 If you’re able, please consider donating to the fund that has been set up to help support Daunte’s family. Please remember that silence is compliance #blacklivesmatter  Link below🙏🏼🕊XoRZ 

https://www.gofundme.com/f/dauntewright

Repost from @meredithmelling
•
It’s heartbreaking to watch Katie Wright, the mother of Daunte Wright, painfully detail her final words with her 20 year old son who called her in fear (rightfully) when he was pulled over by police for a traffic violation and murdered just moments later by one of the officers. Katie Wright will never see her son alive again. This Mother’s Day, I will be donating to The Daunte Wright Sr. Memorial Fund. All funds raised will go towards covering costs related to funeral and burial expenses, mental health and grief counseling, support for Daunte’s son, Daunte Wright Jr., and the Wright family’s fight for justice. Please visit the link in my bio if you’d like to join me in donating. #justicefordauntewright #blacklivesmatter

node.text: I could have talked for hours with @drjakedeutsch about #Covid-19 vaccines 💉 We decided to do an impromptu IG live to help answer all of our questions and apprehensions as well as help spread awareness. I am  sending love and good health to everyone. I hope this was helpful to you all! I am now feeling more confident and ready to get my vaccine when it’s my turn 🙏🏻 ! Please share if you want me to do more medical IG Conversations like this in the future and topics to cover! 🙏🏻❤️XoRZ

node.text: I have forever dreamed of creating my own fragrances. This has been years in the making and they are finally here to share with everyone!  I want to bring you an exclusive behind the scenes of the process of bringing my fragrance dreams to life. ✨🙏🏻 I am beyond excited to share that all FOUR of my full sized fragrances - #WARRIOR, #EMPOWERED, #FEARLESS and #INSTINCT are available now on @shoprachelzoe ✨  All of you powerful women inspired the names of each one because I believe ALL women are stronger than we ever realize. I cannot wait to hear what your favorite scent is so please share! Shop at the tag in my IGTV or at shoprachelzoe.com 💫XoRZ

node.text:
The holidays are always such a glamorous time of year and one of the reasons I will be dressing up my family is to take our annual holiday card photo. In all my years of styling, Skyler and Kaius are by far my toughest clients! With that in mind, I wanted to share with you a few of my go-to styling tips for dressing children during the holidays! Be sure to enter the sweepstakes (link in stories) for a chance to win pieces from my @janieandjack Exclusive Party Collection and @shoprachelzoe plus custom holiday cards from @minted with a value of $1,500. Wishing you all a happy and healthy holiday season. ✨XoRZ #holidays #glamour #janieandjack

node.title: Today is the BEST day @vanjones68 and Character and kindness DO matter.

node.text: As I twirl into my next trip around the ☀️ , I am very emotional and truly overwhelmed with the love from all of you 🙏🏻❤️. I am grateful for so many things but mostly the happiness and love that surrounds me and lifts me up when I need it most. Thank you beyond 🎂💐 #birthdaygirl 💃

node.text: So here we are exactly #30 years later from our first date in kindergarten 😉 my ❤️ @rbermanus. Still madly in love and on our favorite beach where we spent our first summer together.  Our journey has been over half of my life filled with unconditional love above all else. We built our careers separately and now together, we bicker and recover at lightening speed and we created the two most magical little humans that completed us.  I realize today more then ever that love is actually all I need and everything else is a bonus ❤️. You are my safest person and my partner in life and in love #forever and always. Also, THANK YOU for telling me every day for 30 years that I am beautiful, even if I don’t believe you it really helps a girl more then you know 🙏🏻. Happiest Anniversary babe #Iloveyou the most. #thisisus 💕💘
